                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 113.) On the 18th of May I was at Greenwich fair, and saw Watson take this handkerchief from the right-hand pocket of a man who stood looking at Richardson's show, and give it to Angeline—I took Angeline—he dropped it—we called to the gentleman that he had been robbed, but he never came to the station—there was such a crowd, we were pushed away from him directly.</p>
